{"tid":2365753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港藥劑師學會會長建議長者接種復星疫苗　科興疫苗留給年輕人","createTime":"2021-01-14T04:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T07:50:04.000Z","uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c89867b8dd1d5f9ee333a76fb7824b57ef817d7a","tid":2365753,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"香港醫院藥劑師學會會長崔俊明說，德國BioNTech與上海復星合作的疫苗有效率較高，但出現輕微發燒等副作用的機會較大；北京科興疫苗的有效率較低，但副作用亦較小。他認為長者可接種有效率較高的復星疫苗，科興疫苗可留給年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超說，在防控重要關頭，不需要介意小部份人接種疫苗後出現傷風等輕微病徵。"},{"pid":"02a0cf14b875814f2ed0a071b44d9a08ca967c0a","tid":2365753,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">真係放棄左香港年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLiaj9T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLiaj9T.png&h=d5c2f227&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b0b62152ed32f309d5111c49044d5526b73a702","tid":2365753,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570362-20210114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570362-20210114.htm&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c7d79420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570362-20210114.htm&h=eb6ab7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570362-20210114.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a38ff87bfb3e3d8f03d5594b9a3c0500ed114e78","tid":2365753,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:43:13.0